Hi there! I was signed up for the 4pm training today for the Persuasion Text Team. I saw it got cancelled so I watched the recording pinned in the channel <#1298623273566732300> 

The only issue is, the recording doesn’t include the invitation link to join Scale to Win! Would a mod be able to send me an invitation link? Thank you!!
Hi <@1278514638774075444> please click [HERE](https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1298432769516634202) and share your email to get your invite.
Thanks <@568257600228032512> ! When I click the link I get this error screen. I've just completed the quiz and waiting to get access to the rest of the Persuasion Channels, is this why?

Actually click [HERE](https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1298623273566732300) and take the quiz then you will be able to go [HERE](https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1298432769516634202) to share your email.
you should see the channel now.
Perfect, I just had to restart Discord and then it recognized that I'd completed the quiz and allowed me to add my email. Thank you so much for your help Carolyn!
I watched a prerecorded training session for texting but don't know how to access Scale to Win. Please help.

Hi <@1299108639105093742> please click [HERE](https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1298623273566732300) and take the quiz then you will be able to go [HERE](https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1298432769516634202) to share your email to get the invite.
